ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾間銀行先用到銀聯，不過多數便利店嘅櫃員機都係銀聯"},{"pid":"aafa3cb902ff2c058f355ef9a2e5337efaf6cbd9","tid":361904,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"全家都襟到 帶少少錢出機場就得"},{"pid":"48349cea124ad7f1b670e9559117c0a07479c256","tid":361904,"uid":85762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"禁錢去便利店最方便，你張卡有銀聯有開海外提款就得"},{"pid":"12d1330e3fe883df79c51f1ab2362c06e845fdb9","tid":361904,"uid":45161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"啱啱8月頭先㩒完無事"},{"pid":"e7e3a4a1f723fc7b334bfeb3b920d902a1e44aba","tid":361904,"uid":53180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T14:32:14.000Z","msg":"係香港部atm開通海外提款，再set幾時到幾時，去到當地搵有銀聯，atm禁就得。<br />\n本人用中銀，唔同銀行每次手續費都唔同，出發前睇清楚，如果唔帶錢去，一次過禁晒成個旅遊用既錢只係收一次手續費。"},{"pid":"e4b48599b42a74fc1de04dbb425226d4c15ebff7","tid":361904,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"月經<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（其實copy左再update返）<br />\n<br />\n先開海外提款<br />\n<br />\n銀聯 hkd15/次<br />\n恒生 hkd20/次 （4月尾，6月中試完）<br />\n<br />\n斷次收費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每日最高提款ntd20k<br />\n<strong>不過之前有巴打用既櫃員機係可以拎ntd30000</strong><br />\n我暫時未遇到過<br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一定要揀saving account （儲蓄戶口）"},{"pid":"43cce82024457974028820f0e52105cbd1a9a0a8","tid":361904,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月經<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（其實copy左再update返）<br />\n<br />\n先開海外提款<br />\n<br />\n銀聯 hkd15/次<br />\n恒生 hkd20/次 （4月尾，6月中試完）<br />\n<br />\n斷次收費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每日最高提款ntd20k<br />\n<strong>不過之前有巴打用既櫃員機係可以拎ntd30000</strong><br />\n我暫時未遇到過<br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一定要揀saving account （儲蓄戶口）</blockquote><br />\nntd 30000?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s